# ── Frontend (Vite) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Backend API base URL. Leave UNSET for local dev (npm run dev uses the Vite
# proxy to localhost:3001). For a production static build, set it to the
# backend's public URL (named Cloudflare Tunnel hostname or VPS).
# VITE_API_BASE=https://api.hunter.example.com

# ── Backend (Express) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Port the API listens on (default 3001).
# PORT=3001

# Extra browser origins allowed by CORS (comma-separated). Add your deployed
# frontend origin(s) here for production.
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://hunter.pages.dev,https://app.hunter.example.com

# ── Skip-trace provider (optional; see MONETIZATION.md) ─────────
# Without these, contact lookups return "not configured" (no data invented).
# SKIPTRACE_API_URL=
# SKIPTRACE_API_KEY=

# ── DNC scrub provider (optional) ───────────────────────────────
# Without these, phones stay non-callable (compliance fail-closed).
# DNC_API_URL=
# DNC_API_KEY=
